Rating: 4
This made for a first-rate appetizer. My only alteration to the recipe was to quarter the figs (instead of halve) and wrap each with a strip of prosciutto. Even people who claimed to not be fans of figs or goat cheese asked for this recipe.

Rating: 4
I needed something different with an interesting presentation so I tried this. I'm not a huge fan of either figs or goat cheese, soI wimped out on the goat cheese and used half cream cheese instead & added some finely chopped roasted almonds as a garnish. Everyone LOVED it!! The goat cheese fans said that they would have used all goat cheese, but I got many requests for the recipe!

